### Project Description:

##### Introduction:

My initial task was to built User Interface as well as User Experience of the clipper.

##### Clipper:

* Designed a  template of clipper on photoshop.
* Developed User interface as well as User Experience of Clipper by HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
* Integrated the code on the clipper extension. 

##### Maya

* Designed the templates of Maya on photoshop as well as Microsoft PowerPoint.
* Developed User interface by applying Angular Material Design to it.
* Development part is still on the way.

##### Software / Libraries Used:

Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Brackets.io, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, AngularJs, Angular Material Design, Semantic and Materialize.css 
